OL,3,CMan shot in head dies 11 days later
OL,5,FThe family of a man who died 11 days
OL,6,Fafter he was shot in the head said
OL,7,F"communities need to come together" as
OL,8,Fpolice launched a murder investigation.
OL,10,FMohammed Hasan, 28, was shot on
OL,11,FGaythorne Road, Bradford, on 8 July
OL,12,Fand died on Sunday 19 July.
OL,14,FNine people have been arrested over
OL,15,Fthe incident but a manhunt continues
OL,16,Ffor 24-year-old suspect Luqman Khan.
OL,18,FIn a statement, Mr Hasan's family said
OL,19,Fhe was a "loving husband, father, son
OL,20,Fand brother".
