OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1784638108
OL,3,CMan shot in head dies 11 days later
OL,5,F"He would go out of his way to help
OL,6,Fother people. He was the life and soul
OL,7,Fof every room he'd walk into," they
OL,8,Fadded.
OL,10,F"He will be missed by all his family
OL,11,Fand the community.
OL,13,F"Life is often overlooked and
OL,14,Fcommunities need to come together to
OL,15,Fmake sure nothing like this happens
OL,16,Fagain.
OL,18,FHasnain Akhter, 21, has already been
OL,19,Fcharged with attempted murder and
OL,20,Fremanded in custody.
OL,26,@rD@AOUuD@AOU
