OL,3,CMan shot in head dies 11 days later
OL,5,FKhan is believed to have travelled to
OL,6,FSuffolk.
OL,8,FDet Ch Insp Dan Bates, of the West
OL,9,FYorkshire Police Homicide and Major
OL,10,FEnquiry Team, said: "We are determined
OL,11,Fto get justice for (Mr Hasan) and his
OL,12,Ffamily and need people to put aside
OL,13,Fany misplaced loyalties and think
OL,14,Fabout how they would feel if it was
OL,15,Ftheir husband, their son, their
OL,16,Fbrother."
